data.description: Newly Refreshed interior! Motivated seller. 3 bed/2 bath home has numerous , boasting beautiful marble flooring throughout. Woodburning fireplace. Open concept layout offering an inviting space for entertaining and day to day comfort. Furniture pictured comes with the home. An absolutely tranquil neighborhood, with manicured lawns and a private no thru street. Shaded yard with chainlink fencing in the back. Great for entertaining. pets and play time. Large air conditioned shed with lots of possibilities. Workshop, Sheshed or even a small apartment. This desirable area is close to all convienences. Dining, shopping, schools, entertainment and medical services, all nearby. Dont miss out on this opportunity to find your home sweet home!
